lo SmartCloud, a SaaS solution that delivers security cloud services for business. It sells its products through retailers, wholesale distributors, broadcast channels, wireless carriers, and security solution providers, as well as through its website. Arlo Technologies, Inc. was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Carlsbad, California.", "fullTimeEmployees": 376, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Matthew Blake McRae", "age": 51, "title": "CEO & Director", "yearBorn": 1974, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 1768402, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 155973}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Kurtis Joseph Binder", "age": 55, "title": "CFO & COO", "yearBorn": 1970, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 931102, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Brian  Busse J.D.", "age": 56, "title": "General Counsel & Corporate Secretary", "yearBorn": 1969, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 664202, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Samir  Kapoor", "age": 53, "title": "Chief Technology Officer", "yearBorn": 1972, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Lily  Knowles", "title": "Senior Vice President of Marketing & Customer Care", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Antoinette  Switzer", "title": "Senior Vice President of Worldwide Human Resources", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Scott  McManigal", "title": "Senior Vice President of Design & Experience", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Michael A. Werdann", "age": 57, "title": "Chief Revenue Officer", "yearBorn": 1968, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Tahmin  Clarke", "title": "Investor Relations Executive", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}],